description:
Welcome to the February Startup Grind Porto event!
João Moita & Rui Paiva (WeDo Founders) will share their stories and experiences. Take the opportunity to chat with other fellow founders and enjoy the breathtaking view from the Critical Software office. Register now! 
Agenda 
7:00 PM – Welcome drinks and networking
8:00 PM – Fireside chat with João Moita & Rui Paiva
9:00 PM – More networking & making friends
9:30 PM – Event ends
name: João Moita & Rui Paiva (WeDo Founders) at Startup Grind Porto
